## Website Used for Practice

The practice website used in this project is maintained by Elemental Selenium and provides many useful testing examples.

https://the-internet.herokuapp.com/

## Goals

- Improve Selenium automation skills
- Practice writing stable and maintainable test cases
- Understand common UI testing patterns
- Prepare for real-world QA automation scenarios

